{"tid":1458670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解今日機會咁多fake news成功傳開？ 因為傳媒直播全部去晒警隊3個鐘記招","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T00:24:36.000Z","uid":184374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86cfcbf962765498e990b19138a357f5b11f2c5e","tid":1458670,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"今日第一次警隊二哥出嚟<br />\n第一次警方記招唔趕收工、舉行三個鐘<br />\n第一次警方記招有普通話、大陸口音嘅記問問題<br />\n結果4-5點全部直播都係警方記招<br />\n<br />\n然後4點同時間大量fake news流出，無機場直播做fact check，連tg 都極少已fact check資訊流出。9成人信晒斷wifi、斷電話網絡、斷交通、斷冷氣、熄燈、6點清場。<br />\n<br />\n直到5點幾6點先陸續有返機場live、黃之峰1812出fb post澄清機場狀況，但已經大部份人走咗、行緊出東涌。<br />\n<br />\n下次再遇到網絡差嘅時候，真係要好好準備一個有認受性嘅文字直播，尤其係媒體，可能sms比同事再出post轉述現場環境、可能衛星電話？（我無相關知識），最少fact check到現場情況，唔會造成咁大嘅公眾恐慌。"},{"pid":"3e160dd47836612b753f1f835e2dcca3b5b2a0b0","tid":1458670,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔係冇記者做直播，係網絡太差"},{"pid":"fb391f2f9703b1f77be0c8fb3cdbdd882c1a6413","tid":1458670,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"[是日戰績] 半日政府損失 二千五百萬財務業績<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好再塞鐵塞路<br />\n低效率高風險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港，得一個國際機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊記：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有旅客就去，冇旅客就退</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7c585d5b0f8bb3ade6ce8cd6fd9bda35373d18b","tid":1458670,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e160dd47836612b753f1f835e2dcca3b5b2a0b0","tid":1458670,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔係冇記者做直播，係網絡太差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"所以我最尾講，<span style=\"color: red;\">網絡差嘅時候要有一個有認受性嘅文字直播</span>，如果4-5點呢段時間有媒體文字描述現場情況，已經fact check到大部份消息係fake news"},{"pid":"3397e3c9774862b7ea2d0ffcc0f893ff0125bea2","tid":1458670,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c4aecfd6df8a13a725e2c62bf0ceba48b297863","tid":1458670,"uid":167764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"果段時間直播全部轉晒去記者會冇人講機場真係以為斷上網"},{"pid":"e02381c52c48b152e34c36db4eceed3c9dbdbcec","tid":1458670,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4aecfd6df8a13a725e2c62bf0ceba48b297863","tid":1458670,"uid":167764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"果段時間直播全部轉晒去記者會冇人講機場真係以為斷上網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"所以真係諗諗計，再遇類似情況現場網絡差，要整/推到有媒體做文字現場描述"},{"pid":"dc21874a40dbb9811429f0496f0a40f6e95d8979","tid":1458670,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}